{"tid":1062361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我見識到咩叫狗公型毒撚 我知你有上連登","createTime":"2019-03-15T04:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T12:18:14.000Z","uid":79789,"like":22,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"37b16939f00445619413fc4a5a8bcc54adc94874","tid":1062361,"uid":79789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日我女朋友搭268c黎搵我 <br />\n<br />\n咁我次次都會接佢 <br />\n<br />\n見佢落車之後有個男仔撩佢講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我開頭以為問路啦 點知見女朋友個樣尷尷尬尬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我咪拿拿林行快兩步接返佢 問返先知問佢有無IG<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再望返係我地愈行愈快個男仔 <br />\n<br />\n由頭到尾都係個毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個頭仲好似未訓醒咁<br />\n<br />\n唔講我以爲佢頭上有個雀巢係到<br />\n<br />\n有自信係好事 但..勝在你太有自信<br />\n<br />\n個陣真係頂唔撚順 屌柒左佢 執好個樣再撩女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋建議下次柒左掉頭走 唔好係前面愈行愈快<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係九龍灣既巴打們睇實自己女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（唔撚記得影低你條柒頭 <br />\n睇你個撚樣都係有上連登 <br />\n再執過個look啦 <br />\n參與多啲社交活動 <br />\n比多啲興趣自己 唔撚係係巴士諗住撩到女仔下話<br />\n比你撩到都一定唔係咩好女仔<br />\n你估個個咁隨便咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咁樣一定嚇親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n最後講多次 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f1bda31ece2d5ee90a4d4e84409dab2a283409c","tid":1062361,"uid":43061,"like":13,"dislike":29,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"人地問下個女仔有冇ig就比你放上網公審<br />\n叫你條女唔好出街啦 下次有人問佢路 講多2句係咪比你打柒阿?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7e0e8f931c09299f510a773c6fa54b78902cde","tid":1062361,"uid":28603,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"小氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3399746dd3f656c48309b2760c8dcce04ada06","tid":1062361,"uid":145927,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住囉，我執好個樣之後連IG都唔洗問直接搶走你條女啦。為你好咋ching!"},{"pid":"630a1a7375db1a68728d175b34c2f1fbe4f36393","tid":1062361,"uid":2165,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"結論係樓主同條友一樣係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問個ig就好似無左條女咁你都幾無自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676516aafcdc9dfe2ccc76a68914c4e948779970","tid":1062361,"uid":57797,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"你條柒頭唔當面捉住佢黎屌？事後上黎屌有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795045a6021d3e27b88253e6802009121e4233e9","tid":1062361,"uid":173184,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"如果你今日去接既係 坐住另一個男人架林寶堅尼出黎既女朋友 唔知巴打你伯有咩感受？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0de497b2189ec1c5e35f9f55ed446dc3f9a36b","tid":1062361,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:52:08.000Z",